::Skulletron::

	Skulletron listens to Feline's plan.

	"Yes, you're right.  If we went in together they'd get suspicious.  You go
in first and I come an hour or so later.  Got it.  Let's go!" Skulletron
says, running out the entrance, stopping part way and motioning Feline to
follow.
